description:
The Fugitive
S04E23 (#113)
Passage to Helena

FIXED AUDIO - previously seeded versions had very distorted sound
CORRECT ASPECT RATIO - previous versions were very small



After being arrested in a small Montana town for a minor loitering charge, Kimble is put in jail next to a suspect in a race-related killing. A determined black deputy becomes determined to transport Kimble and the racist murderer to the state capital for arraignment. But their journey is filled with adventure and danger when they are ambushed by the killer's accomplices and are now forced to travel on foot through hostile territory.

Writer: Barry Oringer
Director: Richard Benedict

Richard Kimble: David Janssen

Guest star: James Farentino (Carter), Percy Rodriguez (Dalton), Phyllis Love (Laura), Russ Conway (Thornton), J. Pat O'Malley (McGinnis), Garry Walberg (Webster), Michael Mikler (Kline), Gene Kirkwood (Lockett), Orville Sherman (Prewit), Marc Winters (Tom)
